// ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏à‡∏≥‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î‡πÉ‡∏ô modal
document.getElementById("totalAmount").innerText = remainingAmount + " ‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏ó"; 
// ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏à‡∏≥‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏ô modal
document.getElementById("remainingAmount").innerText = remainingAmount + " ‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏ó"; 

